Package: scaRf
Type: Package
Title: Train, use and evaluate SCARF on a given dataset
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "David", "de la Rosa",
      email = "drrosa@ujaen.es",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A set of tools to train and evaluate the SCARF model into a given 
    dataset. You provide the data and create and train a SCARF model using 
    'scarf_fit'. Then, you can use the pretrained model, stored in your machine,
    to extract the latent representations of a given dataset using 
    'scarf_feature_extractor'. The package allows the evaluation of the 
    representations by training a classifier with 
    'train_classifier_on_representations', and the evaluation of the 
    classifier with 'downstream_prediction'.
